title: Ep. - 202 - UNSOLVED MYSTERIES WITH JEN YATES
description:
Medium Jennifer Yates discusses several unsolved mystery cases including the case of John Demjanjuk, a grandfather and retired Ford plant employee living in Cleveland who was accused of being the notorious WWII Nazi concentration camp guard known as Ivan the Terrible, the Delphi murders, the disappearance of Jodi Huisentruit, and Jeffrey Epstein. 



Reality Life with Kate Casey
